[
    {
        "text": "This is Mike Mitchell,\ndirector of \"The Lego Movie",
        "start": 0.5,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "2 —",
        "start": 3.34,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "The Second Part.\"",
        "start": 3.84,
        "duration": 1.53
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 5.37,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "Here we are in\nBricksburg, which",
        "start": 5.87,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "has been destroyed\nby Duplo aliens,",
        "start": 7.38,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "leaving it apocalyptic.",
        "start": 9.51,
        "duration": 1.93
    },
    {
        "text": "And Lucy and Emmet\nand Battlecatty",
        "start": 11.44,
        "duration": 3.95
    },
    {
        "text": "are checking out a new evolved\nalien that’s just arrived,",
        "start": 15.39,
        "duration": 3.54
    },
    {
        "text": "and she spotted Emmet dancing.",
        "start": 18.93,
        "duration": 2.395
    },
    {
        "text": "“Uh, oh.”",
        "start": 21.325,
        "duration": 1.505
    },
    {
        "text": "So it was a real\nchallenge to make",
        "start": 22.83,
        "duration": 3.06
    },
    {
        "text": "sure that in the\nanimation that we could only",
        "start": 25.89,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "use Lego bricks that really\nexist in the real world",
        "start": 28.62,
        "duration": 4.53
    },
    {
        "text": "even though this is all\ndone on the computer.",
        "start": 33.15,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "So we made sure everything\nhas a handmade feel",
        "start": 35.05,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "and that we’re only using\nLego brick for everything",
        "start": 39.69,
        "duration": 3.85
    },
    {
        "text": "including the smoke,\nincluding the dust,",
        "start": 43.54,
        "duration": 2.45
    },
    {
        "text": "including the explosions.",
        "start": 45.99,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "And if you look closely,\neverything’s dusty.",
        "start": 48.09,
        "duration": 1.86
    },
    {
        "text": "Sometimes there’s\nfingerprints on the Lego.",
        "start": 49.95,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "This is them master building\na getaway car, Chris Pratt",
        "start": 53.07,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "and Elizabeth Banks.",
        "start": 56.85,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "“Snazzy racing stripes.”",
        "start": 58.26,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "For this film we’re\ndesigning new things",
        "start": 61.96,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "with our production\ndesigner, Patrick Hanenberger",
        "start": 63.91,
        "duration": 2.23
    },
    {
        "text": "and art director\nKristen Anderson.",
        "start": 66.14,
        "duration": 3.66
    },
    {
        "text": "But we’re also working\nhand in hand with Lego.",
        "start": 69.8,
        "duration": 3.62
    },
    {
        "text": "And as they’re\nbuilding toys, they’re",
        "start": 73.42,
        "duration": 1.74
    },
    {
        "text": "helping us design as well.",
        "start": 75.16,
        "duration": 1.339
    },
    {
        "text": "So it’s like a back\nand forth that we",
        "start": 76.499,
        "duration": 1.541
    },
    {
        "text": "had between our artists and\nour animators and the toy",
        "start": 78.04,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "makers, as well.",
        "start": 81.61,
        "duration": 2.13
    },
    {
        "text": "There’s a blinker gag that I\nstole from a SpongeBob movie,",
        "start": 83.74,
        "duration": 2.65
    },
    {
        "text": "I directed, that was cut out.",
        "start": 86.39,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "And even that stream\nof smoke, everything",
        "start": 90.98,
        "duration": 2.19
    },
    {
        "text": "is made out of a brick.",
        "start": 93.17,
        "duration": 1.59
    },
    {
        "text": "“I can’t believe another\nyear has passed.”",
        "start": 94.76,
        "duration": 2.81
    },
    {
        "text": "“Wrong flare!”",
        "start": 97.57,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "“Should old acquaintance — “",
        "start": 98.98,
        "duration": 3.196
    },
    {
        "text": "“Alfred, battle cars.”",
        "start": 102.176,
        "duration": 2.444
    },
    {
        "text": "“Undeniably, Apocalypseburg\nis a nod to Mad Max",
        "start": 104.62,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "without stealing from Mad Max.",
        "start": 108.94,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "But it was really\nfun to do all",
        "start": 111.16,
        "duration": 1.98
    },
    {
        "text": "these apocalyptic vehicles\nand this dusty look,",
        "start": 113.14,
        "duration": 3.63
    },
    {
        "text": "but all through the\nwhimsical lens of Lego.”",
        "start": 116.77,
        "duration": 3.868
    },
    {
        "text": "[screaming]",
        "start": 120.638,
        "duration": 1.912
    },
    {
        "text": "“We’re alive!",
        "start": 122.55,
        "duration": 1.412
    },
    {
        "text": "Aah!”",
        "start": 123.962,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "“Love you.”",
        "start": 128.286,
        "duration": 1.195
    },
    {
        "text": "“I love you more.",
        "start": 129.481,
        "duration": 1.209
    },
    {
        "text": "These stars and\nhearts are voiced",
        "start": 130.69,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "by the children of our\neditors, Wyatt Jones",
        "start": 132.13,
        "duration": 2.64
    },
    {
        "text": "and Claire Knight.",
        "start": 134.77,
        "duration": 1.71
    },
    {
        "text": "And I believe they’re\naround seven years",
        "start": 136.48,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "old when we recorded them.”",
        "start": 138.7,
        "duration": 1.89
    },
    {
        "text": "“Wee!”",
        "start": 140.59,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "“Hello!”",
        "start": 141.79,
        "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
        "text": "“Hurray!”",
        "start": 142.79,
        "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
        "text": "[grunts]",
        "start": 149.59,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "[whimpers]",
        "start": 151.39,
        "duration": 1.85
    }
]